{
  "title": "Crunchy Roasted Italian Chicken Pasta",
  "description": "A springy weeknight Italian dish featuring roasted chicken and pasta, with a unique twist of Marmite flavor, made easy with air fryer and dash-friendly ingredients.",
  "cuisine": "Italian",
  "diet": [
    "gluten-free",
    "low-sodium"
